Mojang implements certain procedures to help protect children and their privacy including complying with the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) and General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).

You may need to obtain parental consent before accessing your Realms account.

If you have an older Minecraft account (you log in with your username), you need to migrate the account to a Mojang account in order to access Realms.

chatPreview.tooltip.confirm:
If a server uses Chat Previews: A chat preview is only generated when attempting to send a message that does not have a preview or is waiting for a preview.
Sending the message requires confirmation.
chatPreview.tooltip.live: If a server uses Chat Previews: Any modifications applied to your chat messages by a server will be dynamically sent for previewing as the chat message is typed.
chatPreview.tooltip.off: Any modifications applied to your chat messages by a server will not be previewed and will be treated as insecure.
